Mi Ra and Kim Dong Hyun beat Wang Shi-Ting and Lien Yu-Hui of Chinese
Taipei 6-4, 6-4.
</P>
<P>
It was the first time in Universiade tennis history that all the
five gold medals were taken by Asian players. 
