is willing to lead the country in a period of transition from the
20th century to the 21st century," Moestahid said.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, United Development Party (PPP), one of the three
political parties in the country, expressed reluctance to follow
in Golkar's footsteps in announcing its presidential nominee now,
with seven months left before the actual presidential election.
