have been waging a 14-year war for a separate state, according to
police sources here today.
</P>
<P>
Colombo's underworld are involved in the drug and bootlegging
trade, internecine and contact killings and extortion.
</P>
<P>
the sources said Police suspicions were aroused when they
detected several sophisticated weapons possessed by 14 underworld
criminal who were rounded up recently.
</P>
<P>
