associated with the rebels.
</P>
<P>
The free movement of these underworld members to and from India
is suspected to have put them in touch with the Liberation Tigers
of Tamil Eelam (LTTE).
</P>
<P>
The LTTE is familiar with the sea routes between India and Sri
Lanka and the underworld members are suspected to use these routes
in their collaboration with the rebels.
</P>
<P>
