<HEADLINE> Rome Open to Ankara's European Objective </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, August 26 (Xinhua) -- Italian Foreign Minister Lamberto
Dini lent measured support today to Turkey's European Union
ambitions after a meeting here with his Turkish counterpart Ismail
Cem.
