distinct "entities" on the island, Turkish Cypriots and Greek
Cypriots, and that both had to be included in talks on the
island's future membership of the EU.
</P>
<P>
He argued that it would be a mistake if Brussels were to
negotiate only with the Greek Cypriot administration in Nicosia.
